    public interface UniqueNamedSBase
extends NamedSBase, UniqueSId
    This interface is used to tag all those elements whose identifier must be unique within an SBML Model before SBML Level 3 Version 2. Since Level 2 Version 1 UnitDefinitions are allowed to have their own id-name space. Therefore, UnitDefinitions should not implement this interface introducing an additional check for Level 1 models.

    To identified elements whose identifier must be unique for SBML Level 3 Version 2 or above, we created the interface UniqueSId.
